117
00:06:03,330 --> 00:06:04,464
Back in the day,

118
00:06:04,531 --> 00:06:07,667
what we now call
budae-jjigae restaurants

119
00:06:07,734 --> 00:06:10,871
were actually all budae barbecue houses.

120
00:06:10,937 --> 00:06:13,340
Back in the day, budae-jjigae restaurants

121
00:06:13,406 --> 00:06:17,143
-were all budae barbecue houses.
-Budae barbecue?

122
00:06:17,210 --> 00:06:19,312
-The sauces and meats that came from…
-Yes.

123
00:06:19,813 --> 00:06:21,915
…the U.S. military bases

124
00:06:21,982 --> 00:06:24,050
were all sold here, along with the stew.

125
00:06:24,117 --> 00:06:26,720
So back then, the term budae-jjigae
wasn't really used.

126
00:06:26,786 --> 00:06:29,656
Every time a new president
came into office,

127
00:06:29,723 --> 00:06:32,959
-the name would change, like Johnson-tang.
-Johnson-tang. Right.

128
00:06:33,026 --> 00:06:35,128
Yes, that's how it went,

129
00:06:35,195 --> 00:06:38,698
until the name budae-jjigae
eventually became standardized.

