268
00:14:06,779 --> 00:14:09,148
It's not like it'll disappear
the moment I open it.

269
00:14:09,215 --> 00:14:11,984
No, we'll have to start all over again.

270
00:14:13,419 --> 00:14:18,391
Does the owner really know
what's happening inside the pot?

271
00:14:18,458 --> 00:14:19,892
There's a timer. He knows.

272
00:14:19,959 --> 00:14:21,027
-He's there, right?
-Yes.

273
00:14:21,561 --> 00:14:22,595
He's coming back now.

274
00:14:26,199 --> 00:14:28,201
Your food's ready.

275
00:14:28,267 --> 00:14:29,869
So this is how it's served.

276
00:14:33,005 --> 00:14:34,974
-Kimchi.
-It's kimchi.

277
00:14:35,041 --> 00:14:38,111
We cut the kimchi
right before it's brought to the table.

278
00:14:48,721 --> 00:14:52,091
He just opened it and mixed it.

279
00:14:52,158 --> 00:14:55,595
I was about to say something
about what's in the pot,

280
00:14:55,661 --> 00:14:57,497
but I couldn't say anything.

281
00:14:57,930 --> 00:15:00,366
Please wait just a moment.
I'll let you know when it's ready.

282
00:15:00,433 --> 00:15:01,901
-What did he say?
-Wait a bit more.

283
00:15:01,968 --> 00:15:03,503
-Not yet?
-Not yet.

284
00:15:03,569 --> 00:15:05,271
Not yet…

285
00:15:05,338 --> 00:15:08,708
-He'll tell us when it's done.
-I see, all right.

286
00:15:09,142 --> 00:15:13,045
As long as he doesn't forget.

287
00:15:14,614 --> 00:15:17,950
-We can't have the kimchi either?
-You can.

288
00:15:18,017 --> 00:15:20,253
-I can?
-Go ahead.

289
00:15:23,990 --> 00:15:25,491
It's good.

290
00:15:34,267 --> 00:15:36,269
See how serious he is.

291
00:15:41,107 --> 00:15:42,708
All done. You can eat now.

